      • getRelatedId

        private java.lang.String getRelatedId(SBase sb)
        Returns an id depending of the type of SBase given. If it is a Reaction, returns reaction.id, if it is an Assignment, returns assignment.variable (symbol or variable attribute), if it is a Species, returns species.compartment. For any other type of SBase, returns null.
